OL,3,CVictims of bankrupt funeral companies
OL,4,Cleft with nothing - is your plan safe?
OL,6,FPeople who bought funeral plans from
OL,7,Fcompanies that collapsed have told ITV
OL,8,FNews they are calling for a public
OL,9,Finquiry.
OL,11,FSafe Hands Plans Limited and One Life
OL,12,FFuneral Planning left tens of
OL,13,Fthousands of customers without
OL,14,Ffunerals - and without the money
OL,15,Fthey've paid.
OL,17,FAfter struggling to pay for her
OL,18,Fhusband's final arrangements,
OL,19,FChristine Hughes, 77, paid for her own
OL,20,Ffuneral.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
