OL,3,CVictims of bankrupt funeral companies
OL,4,Cleft with nothing - is your plan safe?
OL,6,FShe did it for peace of mind, but what
OL,7,Fshe has got is worry. The company Safe
OL,8,FHands Plans Ltd went bust two years
OL,9,Fago.
OL,11,F"It cost me #4095, and it was
OL,12,Fbasically all the money that I've got
OL,13,Fin the bank. When I paid for my
OL,14,Ffuneral plan, I had about #100 left,"
OL,15,FChristine told ITV News.
OL,17,F"I wanted a proper send off so my
OL,18,Ffamily could say goodbye properly. Now
OL,19,Fthat's not going to happen because I
OL,20,Fcan't get that money again to pay for
OL,21,Fanother funeral."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
