OL,3,CVictims of bankrupt funeral companies
OL,4,Cleft with nothing - is your plan safe?
OL,6,FChristine said she felt others like
OL,7,Fher hadn't been supported in the wake
OL,8,Fof Safe Hands Plans Ltd's collapse.
OL,10,FShe said: "I feel hurt, I do feel let
OL,11,Fdown and I think I speak for many
OL,12,Fpeople when I say we feel that we've
OL,13,Fjust been pushed to one side and
OL,14,Fnobody's interested."
OL,16,FITV News has learned that the
OL,17,Fadministrators of the collapsed Safe
OL,18,FHands Plans Ltd are about to make an
OL,19,Fannouncement on available funds - but
OL,20,Fit's expected to be only a fraction of
OL,21,Fwhat plan holders paid.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
