OL,11,FIs your funeral plan safe?
OL,13,FFinancial campaigner James Daley from
OL,14,FFairer Finance says officials should
OL,15,Fhave known money was at risk and
OL,16,Fshould have acted.
OL,18,FHe said: "Many people are still
OL,19,Funaware they have got plans that are
OL,20,Fworth nothing.
