OL,6,F"It is time that the government steps
OL,7,Fup and says, 'We let a lot of people
OL,8,Fdown here, let's look at why that
OL,9,Fhappened, make sure it never happens
OL,10,Fagain in any other sector, and try to
OL,11,Fhelp those people who have already
OL,12,Fpaid for a funeral'."
OL,14,FThe latest estimates reckon one in six
OL,15,Ffunerals are now paid for via a
OL,16,Ffuneral plan.
