OL,3,CVictims of bankrupt funeral companies
OL,4,Cleft with nothing - is your plan safe?
OL,6,FAny bought after July 2022 from
OL,7,Fauthorised providers will be protected
OL,8,Fby the Financial Services Compensation
OL,9,FScheme - this means your money is
OL,10,Fprotected if the company fails.
OL,12,FYou can check whether your funeral
OL,13,Fplan is covered by Financial Conduct
OL,14,FAuthority (FCA) compensation rules
OL,15,Fhere.
OL,17,FThe FCA website also has warnings
OL,18,Fabout funeral plan firms that did not
OL,19,Fbecome authorised, and therefore
OL,20,Fshould not be selling plans.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
