OL,3,CVictims of bankrupt funeral companies
OL,4,Cleft with nothing - is your plan safe?
OL,6,FWe asked finance campaigner James
OL,7,FDaley of Fairer Finance to give some
OL,8,Ftips for those buying funerals in
OL,9,Fadvance.
OL,11,FFairer Finance's James Daley gives a
OL,12,Fbreakdown of what to consider when
OL,13,Fbuying a funeral plan
OL,15,FCheck that the firm is FCA regulated
OL,17,FTo make sure of this, look on the
OL,18,FFCA's register. If the company is on
OL,19,Fthere, then you can buy with
OL,20,Fconfidence and know your money will be
OL,21,Fprotected if the firm goes bust.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
