OL,4,Cleft with nothing - is your plan safe?
OL,6,FBe sure of what is covered on the
OL,7,Ffuneral plan
OL,9,FThere is a lot of difference in the
OL,10,Fmarket. Some guarantee all the core
OL,11,Fcosts, such as the cost of a
OL,12,Fcrematorium.
OL,14,FOthers, such as a contribution plan,
OL,15,Fjust have a pot of money to put
OL,16,Ftowards those third-party costs.
OL,18,FStay aware of flexibility
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
